translated: Melbäck, Karl Sven Börje, is a retired customs officer, born on August 11th, 1917 in Filipstad. Married in 1945 to Inga-Lis Andersson. They have one child, Bo, born in 1946. Karl worked as a city police officer in Södervärnsvägen from 1944 to 1946, and later as a customs officer in Tranås in 1946.
